headline: 3 Reasons Investors Love Wabtec (WAB)
summary: Wabtec trades at $168.33 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 10.4% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 9.8%. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
